channel.title: Server starting problem
channel.description: Here is my problem. I edited my shop name, and then compiled. I started server, and it said a bunch of stuff never before. I tried to get on, took time to load, and then exited me. I looked on the server window, and it said im already logged on, low memeroy version. Whats the problem?
